{"tid":1391713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣朋友對香港人的忠告:","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:53:50.000Z","uid":73092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"961841356b63e435f3265c2826a438a0e3d2308a","tid":1391713,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"台灣朋友對香港人的忠告:<br />\n給香港朋友。<br />\n面對鎮暴水車，還沒被沖到以前你想像是加強版SPA，但其實被沖到就是像拿木棍在戳你，會內臟翻騰兩三天，沒有正面抵抗的辦法，但穿戰術背心會有緩衝效果，保護你的內臟。<br />\n不要停留，保持距離，不要像照片一樣坐下來，但小心奔跑時被衝到，跌倒會加重受傷。盡可能全罩安全帽保護你的眼睛，水來時一定要背對，蹲馬步沒有用，水來還是倒。<br />\n製作雞爪釘，每個游擊者在撤退的時候撒下一把又一把，拖延水車前進時間，往下一個戰場移動。<br />\n保護你的眼睛，噴到會爆。<br />\n小心裡面裝不明液體，準備好沖洗的乾淨水源。<br />\n祝港人平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@Sunanmoonnew1/102535178775212997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmastodon.social%2F%40Sunanmoonnew1%2F102535178775212997&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6426715b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mastodon.social/@Sunanmoonnew1/102535178775212997</a>"},{"pid":"171353c442646cb3dc2afa30e3eb2b23fcdb0867","tid":1391713,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第一波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a81862a0bbdf01c1e6cfd00fce11cd6d64aed4d","tid":1391713,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"f535ad9d25104cce81eadcac7f01a077b9ef91ce","tid":1391713,"uid":196535,"lik